com.paypal.selion.grid

Interface LauncherOptions

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ProcessLauncherOptions
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LauncherConfiguration, ProcessLauncherConfiguration

    public interface LauncherOptions
    These options give a programmatic way to influence some of the behaviors of a RunnableLauncher. These behaviors may or may not have a SeLion Grid dash argument that corresponds to them. Dash arguments override LauncherOptions.
